<div id="articles-header">
  <div class="container-info">
    <h4>Last month in short</h4><br>
    <p>We settled in <i>Iceland, Bali, Italian Switzerland, Valencia</i> and <i>Asmara</i>.</p>
    <p class="lozenge">&#8977;</p>
    <p>Video traces of our presence can be found in our last vlog.</p>
    <p class="lozenge">&#8977;</p>
    <p>Follow us @settler and see the world through our smartphone's reer cameras.</p>
    <p class="lozenge">&#8977;</p>
    <p>Our newsletter is delivered on Saturdays and includes our latest stories as well as a curated selection of geographic tales from other explorers worldwide. <br> <%= link_to "Be sure to subscribe", subscribers_path %>.</p>
